			<div class="caption">
									
					<h2 class="block-title">
													<div class="subtitle">About the Author</div>
												Alexandra Stafford					</h2>
						
				<p>Alexandra (Ali) Stafford is the founder of Alexandra’s Kitchen and the author of two cookbooks: <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Bread Toast Crumbs</span> and The New York Times bestselling <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Pizza Night</span>. She lives in Upstate New York with her husband, four children, 3 cats, and 1 dog.</p>
				
